<figureCitation box="[633,699,1578,1602]" captionStart="FIGURE 7. A – L" captionStartId="15.[151,250,1819,1842]" captionTargetBox="[209,1377,193,1773]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[209,1377,193,1774]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 7. A – L. Tugonia (Distugonia) sp., A – I, L, MBM 188705, length = 9 mm. A. Exterior of right valve. B. Exterior of left valve. Scale bar (A, B) = 2 mm. C. Hinge of right valve. Scale bar = 1 mm. D. Interior of right valve. E. Interior of left valve. Scale bar (D, E) = 2 mm. F. Hinge of left valve. Scale bar = 1 mm. G. Close up of umbo on right valve. H. Close up of umbo on left valve. Scale bar (G, H) = 1 mm. I. Close up of surface sculpture. Scale bar = 1 mm. L. Dorsal view of both valves joined. Scale bar = 2 mm. J &amp; K, MBM 188706, length = 7.60 mm. J. Exterior of right valve. K. Interior of right valve. Scale bar (J, K) = 2 mm. M. Tugonia (Distugonia) decurtata (A. Adams, 1851) (after original figure from Sowerby II, 1875: pl. 3, fig. 11). N – O. Tugonia (Distugonia) inopinata (Iredale, 1936) (after original figure from Iredale, 1936: pl. 21, figs. 6, 7)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/281741/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="53">
Fig. 
<number box="[685,699,1579,1602]" pageId="14" pageNumber="53" value="7.0">7</number>
</figureCitation>
N, O; see also 
<bibRefCitation author="Lamprell" box="[861,1159,1578,1602]" pageId="14" pageNumber="53" refString="Lamprell, K. &amp; Stanisic, J. (1998) Myidae from Australian waters (Mollusca, Bivalvia). Molluscan Research, 19 (1), 1 - 10." type="journal article" year="1998">
Lamprell &amp; Stanisic, 
<number box="[1099,1159,1578,1602]" pageId="14" pageNumber="53" value="1998.0">1998</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number box="[1169,1185,1579,1602]" pageId="14" pageNumber="53" value="7.0">7</number>
, fig. 
<number box="[1241,1255,1578,1602]" pageId="14" pageNumber="53" value="4.0">4</number>
a–d) by its more regular shell; the rather concave posterodorsal margin of 
<taxonomicName authority="Iredale, 1936" authorityName="Iredale" authorityYear="1936" box="[797,986,1614,1639]" class="Bivalvia" family="Myidae" genus="Distugonia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Myida" pageId="14" pageNumber="53" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="inopinata" subGenus="Distugonia">
<emphasis box="[797,986,1614,1639]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="53">T. (D.) inopinata</emphasis>
